{"tid":608624,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"學術討論下點解大陸人中意拍''幹片''?","createTime":"2018-03-28T10:03:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T19:46:56.000Z","uid":70429,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"fb5ce1b9aefefe4091393dd976a92acfe64e52a3","tid":608624,"uid":70429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T10:03:07.000Z","msg":"首先,<br />\n<br />\n''幹片'' 姐係果d<span style=\"color: red;\">主角係大集團老闆 or CEO但扮廢/扮窮/咁岩自己單獨行開/同學會然後比舊同學/舊朋友/前拜金女友/以前恰佢既人睇唔起,最後表露身份大翻睇唔起佢既人. 想帶出切勿狗眼看人低既道理</span>.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實條片無論內容定故事都係千篇一律而且極度低質.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喺外國都有youtuber中意拍類似依d既片,<br />\n<br />\n例如話一開始扮流浪漢,比餐廳趕走之後渣架法拉利去間餐廳門口串翻人.<br />\n<br />\nor渣架日本車去搭訕女仔,比女仔拒絕之後再渣架林寶去搭訕翻同一個女仔.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我只係好奇究竟依d內容既片究竟點解吸引到人???<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f0254ff44c083d2bba72d463ed49d63a6a23e7","tid":608624,"uid":64009,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T10:05:25.000Z","msg":"因為自卑"},{"pid":"cc22a24eea8607e7b7e81b36f8a9921428b0d65b","tid":608624,"uid":121333,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T10:07:09.000Z","msg":"因為有代入感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"383d6295257e253e84fa08cffdca285689bf22f3","tid":608624,"uid":46943,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T10:07:48.000Z","msg":"因為想道出有錢點玩都得呢個道理"},{"pid":"b53423d38792f613a77a8f343c0474c173f9e3b6","tid":608624,"uid":135767,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T10:09:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"389812f1e16ff06783b36b482f5e6bed02825311","tid":608624,"uid":1255,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"383d6295257e253e84fa08cffdca285689bf22f3","tid":608624,"uid":46943,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T10:07:48.000Z","msg":"因為想道出有錢點玩都得呢個道理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T10:10:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass